alerts.description:
There is a risk of heavy persistent rain (level 3 of 4).
Precipitation amounts: 40-60 l/m²; in windward areas: < 100 l/m²

There is a risk of storm-force gusts (level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 80-95 km/h; Wind direction: south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 115 km/h

There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Max. gusts: < 60 km/h; Wind direction: south then south-west; Increased gusts: near showers and in exposed locations ~ 65 km/h
